WEBVTT

00:03:27.342 --> 00:03:30.795
kusikia mawazo mapya ya
kustaajabisha na vumbuzi

00:03:30.819 --> 00:03:32.575
na kweli, kuhusu njia zote

00:03:32.599 --> 00:03:35.922
ambazo maarife yanasukumwa
mbele sana.

00:03:36.797 --> 00:03:40.026
Lakini kuna hatua, maarifa yanaondoka.

00:03:40.802 --> 00:03:42.026
Na huo ndio muda

00:03:42.050 --> 00:03:44.685
ambao maisha yako yanaamua kweli:

00:03:45.825 --> 00:03:47.507
unapata upendo;

00:03:48.093 --> 00:03:49.928
unapoteza rafiki;

00:03:50.893 --> 00:03:52.465
taa zinazimika.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:58.014
Na ni hapo, ambapo ukiwa umepotea,
au huelewi au umepoteza matumaini,

00:03:58.038 --> 00:04:00.200
ndipo unapogundua wewe ni nani.